            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:24px;flex-wrap:wrap">
                <div>
                    <h2 style="font-size:36px;margin:0 0 12px">Turn any API/DB into an agent‑safe tool — no code</h2>
                    <p style="color:#9ba3b7;margin:0">Paste an endpoint, get an MCP‑ready tool with schema pins and policy hooks. Publish once to MCP / Copilot / Functions.</p>
